b5e233613fc25985070d746c0","tid":374174,"uid":123969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:26:23.000Z","msg":"香港個闊度同個距離都差不多<br />\n根本都係打都正一正"},{"pid":"0f465f3db5663d3f9e76d196aa3282326c35fce6","tid":374174,"uid":127569,"like":66,"dislike":3,"score":63,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:28:21.000Z","msg":"咁係遠啦，一個第一世界，一個第三世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25d2fc55b2ed76f42e5796457ed838372ae3605b","tid":374174,"uid":33826,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:29:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港個闊度同個距離都差不多<br />\n根本都係打都正一正</blockquote><br />\n我記得中學啲老師講過，打風吹正一個地方時有一刻會係好平靜，因為果時處於風眼位置，反而風眼旁邊所受到颱風環流帶所影響風力先係最勁受害最大<br />\n<br />\n個個都天佑澳門咁有冇人可以天佑下大澳、鯉魚門、杏花村呢啲地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d911ee871a3cb545d31826fe1b804c24eb16a21","tid":374174,"uid":2707,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:32:54.000Z","msg":"點解會諗咗去打唔打得正<br />\n而唔係下澳門點解會水浸成咁，香港就冇咩事(最大鑊都係個停車場仔)<br />\n根本係排水系統都有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b081a9d06f87ffc4af84ea6f84fca87a934afc5","tid":374174,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:33:27.000Z","msg":"鳳凰山頂可以望到澳門<br />\n<br />\n都唔係BVR"},{"pid":"52e2f317756c03ec0b3138451ba55a179b49cfd3","tid":374174,"uid":2707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:33:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解會諗咗去打唔打得正<br />\n而唔係<span style=\"color: red;\">諗</span>下澳門點解會水浸成咁，香港就冇咩事(最大鑊都係個停車場仔)<br />\n根本係排水系統都有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"2118e6a342d4bda0a1bc83c74f425fa61914e6b9","tid":374174,"uid":65406,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:33:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qfMsHaifBWY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqfMsHaifBWY&d=RlaQ%2Fiq9qU2E4FC%2FJh44NQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=e1961a77\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qfMsHaifBWY</a><br />\n<br />\n真係差好遠,感謝黨"},{"pid":"c1466832b77ceb8800673c3654d700aac0fe6dd9","tid":374174,"uid":120908,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:36:59.000Z","msg":"香港一年打幾多個 澳門一年打幾多個<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3ba63f00d7e94bae98b10aa04a69bc1c8c726b1","tid":374174,"uid":12599,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:37:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>見有啲澳門人話今次我地香港人死好彩個風打唔正、唔係係香港登陸，講到個風吹正澳門香港就冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有啲澳門人仲話個風打唔正香港我地唔會明打風嘅痛苦，咁大澳、杏花村呢啲地方就冇事咩？<br />\n<br />\n有冇連登仔可以答下小弟香港同澳門所隔嘅距離究竟有幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ngoogle 下啦<br />\n62~63 公里呀</blockquote><br />\n咁係咪62-63公里嘅相距就可以令我地完全唔會受到今次打風嘅影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實香港今次極好運,最近果下支旋臂岩岩無雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n澳門食正北眼壁,果度係最大風,佢地市中心陣風220km/h, 香港得昂坪有223km/hr,港內風力細好多<br />\n<br />\n香港地形有山勢檔風,加上基建好同civil standard仲把到關,石門有棟新起(中國建築)爆左好多玻璃,澳門有棟偽豪宅全爆又係中國建築<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有一個就係官也街M記vs梅窩M記, 香港果個就食正D浪完全無事,澳門果個內街都玻璃全爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54ad26b2870f9daf407a11e836b0532819f6a519","tid":374174,"uid":33826,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:42:20.000Z","msg":"香港今次受災情況，話就話香港整體地區冇事但其實唔少地方都有受到災害，當然如果垃圾澳門肯早啲掛8號，至少我諗唔洗死咁多人先<br />\n<br />\n大澳<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/cz7ywsmp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fcz7ywsmp&h=8b104294&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/29qiuy8j\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F29qiuy8j&h=6fcd727a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n杏花村<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/thc1qrb2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fthc1qrb2&h=e181ead3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鯉魚門<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/trmh2upc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ftrmh2upc&h=52d13bf4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6213a69e0407110a5156110e5bdaada4c493f90d","tid":374174,"uid":55981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:44:08.000Z","msg":"真心問香港有無地下第四層停車場?<br />\n大商場有無?"},{"pid":"d427d959572b6144109eef770f466c163175310d","tid":374174,"uid":65406,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:44:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>見有啲澳門人話今次我地香港人死好彩個風打唔正、唔係係香港登陸，講到個風吹正澳門香港就冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有啲澳門人仲話個風打唔正香港我地唔會明打風嘅痛苦，咁大澳、杏花村呢啲地方就冇事咩？<br />\n<br />\n有冇連登仔可以答下小弟香港同澳門所隔嘅距離究竟有幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ngoogle 下啦<br />\n62~63 公里呀</blockquote><br />\n咁係咪62-63公里嘅相距就可以令我地完全唔會受到今次打風嘅影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實香港今次極好運,最近果下支旋臂岩岩無雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n澳門食正北眼壁,果度係最大風,佢地市中心陣風220km/h, 香港得昂坪有223km/hr,港內風力細好多<br />\n<br />\n香港地形有山勢檔風,加上基建好同civil standard仲把到關,石門有棟新起(中國建築)爆左好多玻璃,澳門有棟偽豪宅全爆又係中國建築<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有一個就係官也街M記vs梅窩M記, 香港果個就食正D浪完全無事,澳門果個內街都玻璃全爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n路遙知馬力,聽聞澳門賭場幾十年未試過唔做生意.<br />\n真係幾十年都未食過大風?"},{"pid":"20e65b59077b4a62630bf98594d2bf8da1cd8d3a","tid":374174,"uid":33826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:44:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真心問香港有無地下第四層停車場?<br />\n大商場有無?</blockquote><br />\n朗豪坊我記得有B3"},{"pid":"0d76e9413467f2e5920cad967d8cd5ab2e27591c","tid":374174,"uid":36035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:46:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a2704d232417e11d552943840ad708435e0bb0d5","tid":374174,"uid":65406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:49:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>真心問香港有無地下第四層停車場?<br />\n大商場有無?</blockquote><br />\n朗豪坊我記得有B3</blockquote><br />\n香港市區防洪設施做得夠足.都唔知比左幾多錢<br />\n呢壇野比較有印象<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%B7%91%E9%A6%AC%E5%9C%B0%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%8B%E8%93%84%E6%B4%AA%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%25B7%2591%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%259C%25B0%25E4%25B8%258B%25E8%2593%2584%25E6%25B4%25AA%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583&d=RlaQ%2Fiq9qU2E4FC%2FJh44NQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=ae498fb3\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%B7%91%E9%A6%AC%E5%9C%B0%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%8B%E8%93%84%E6%B4%AA%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83</a><br />\n<br />\n所以成個香港得番D低窪地區好難攪既地區仲有事"},{"pid":"d8ca202f4a9010027241d1e3b84b1f9aaaa4b372","tid":374174,"uid":33826,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:58:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>真心問香港有無地下第四層停車場?<br />\n大商場有無?</blockquote><br />\n朗豪坊我記得有B3</blockquote><br />\n香港市區防洪設施做得夠足.都唔知比左幾多錢<br />\n呢壇野比較有印象<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%B7%91%E9%A6%AC%E5%9C%B0%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%8B%E8%93%84%E6%B4%AA%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%25B7%2591%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%259C%25B0%25E4%25B8%258B%25E8%2593%2584%25E6%25B4%25AA%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583&d=RlaQ%2Fiq9qU2E4FC%2FJh44NQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=ae498fb3\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%B7%91%E9%A6%AC%E5%9C%B0%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%8B%E8%93%84%E6%B4%AA%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83</a><br />\n<br />\n所以成個香港得番D低窪地區好難攪既地區仲有事</blockquote><br />\n其實真係好諷刺，以澳門嘅經濟能力絕對可以有錢做好啲防洪設施，就算本身地理環境有缺陷，但相信有錢呢啲問題一定有得搞。至於個風點勁呢個問題，香港以前都試過打十號嫁啦，風嘅程度理論上唔會比唔上，今次澳門咁大件事好大程度係政府垃圾"},{"pid":"aa29a7939bdc1d8b737fceb337733512e5719078","tid":374174,"uid":3476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:25:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>真心問香港有無地下第四層停車場?<br />\n大商場有無?</blockquote><br />\n朗豪坊我記得有B3</blockquote><br />\n西九龍中心有B5"},{"pid":"d49ee67df45795acf3cfd73cf59f9e8de85941fd","tid":374174,"uid":33826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T21:05:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"569f14f60b317f4634ba6a7a6b89f213c8940494","tid":374174,"uid":55732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T22:48:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>見有啲澳門人話今次我地香港人死好彩個風打唔正、唔係係香港登陸，講到個風吹正澳門香港就冇事<img src=\"/assets/fa